We are very fortunate to have a doctor like Dr.Sameera for our son. What I like about Dr.Sameera is her vast experience *** ******** ** ********** ****** ** ****** **** ** **** *** ********** She never prescribes unnecessary medicine and tests. She very patiently listens to concerns and gives great feedback to parents.

It also amazes me that she remembers everything about my son even if I visit after 6 months and will enquire about his overall progress.

I would very highly recommend Dr.Sameera as a paediatrician for every kid :)

I am lucky to have my baby under Dr Sameera's care since his birth. My son was born prematurely. Dr Sameera was very prompt with her NICU timing, patiently answered all our queries, provided every info required in caring for premature baby. Talking to her was a great relief and assuring for us in those tested times. 
At OPD she is punctual, listens very patiently* ********* ******* *** prescribes minimal medication. Never prescribed unnecessary test.Every visit she tracks milestones, vaccination and guides about govt immunization program .With her smiling face and assuring nature baby care has been effortless for me in terms of medical aspects.

My daughter is premature. We always make sure her treatment is done under **** doctor. Recently we relocated to another place in Bangalore. So our first concern was to search a good doctor r for our daughter. Then through online search and seeing her reviews we visited her when my daughter was sick again because of seasonal change. And first visit only we had a sigh of relief that we found **** Doctor for our daughter. I am writing this review so that like me many parents who r searching for good doctor can be benefited.

Dr Sameera is my son’s paediatrician since his birth 3.9 years ago. She’s the reason I could get my infant boy off bottle feeds and get him completely on mom’s milk! I was stunned when I received a text from her, as a new Mom, checking on how I was doing!!! Visits to her clinic are few but it almost feels like dropping in on a family friend’s home! 

She’s a doctor with a heart and her only passion seems like adding value with her expertise. What I love the most about her, she doesn’t rush you through with the appointment, super patient to answer the silliest of questions! I would definitely recommend her to anyone looking for genuine doctors in the Paediatrics  and Neo Natal segment.
